<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title><%= %></%=></title><link rel=stylesheet href=/css/style.css><link rel=stylesheet href=/css/mycss.css><style>
        textarea {
            width: 60%;
            height: 80px;
            padding: 1em;
            resize: none;
            overflow-x: none;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
    </style></head><body><%- include header.ejs %><div class="content main-content"><div id=main><div id=msgshow><a name=leavemsg></a><div class=top><span class=title>留言板</span> [ 认识或不认识我的朋友,留下你的脚印吧... ]</div><div id=publish_comment><input type=hidden id=HideId name=id> <input type=hidden id=HideUser value=biyaoyao><div class=user>姓 名: <input type=text name=user id=user size=30></div><div class=userNum>内 容: [ 留言长度不能超过<span>500</span>个字符 ]<br></div><div class=word><textarea maxlength=500 id=content></textarea></div><div class=error></div><div class=sub><span id=sub><input type=button value=给我留言 onclick=leaveMsg();></span> 注:请珍惜我的成果,文明留言</div></div><a name=more></a><div class=bottom><span class=title>网友留言</span> [ 留下联系方式，我将定期回复你的留言 ]</div><div class=net_msg><%for(var i="0;i<leavList.length;i++){" %><div class=info><div class=num><%=i+1%></%=i+1%></div><div class=user><%=leavlist[i].user%></%=leavlist[i].user%></div><div class=dc_time><%=leavlist[i].create_time%></%=leavlist[i].create_time%></div><div class=op></div><br></div><div id="msg <%=i+1%>" class=com_cont><%=leavlist[i].content%></%=leavlist[i].content%></div><%}%></%}%></%for(var></div></div></div></div><%- include foot.ejs %><script type=text/javascript>
                function leaveMsg() {


                    var user = $("#user").val();
                    var content = $("#content").val();
                    $.getJSON("leaveMsg.action", {
                            user: user,
                            content: content
                        },
                        function (data) {
                            if (data.result) {
                                alert("留言成功！");
                                location.reload();
                            } else {
                                alert(data.tips);
                            }
                        }
                    );

                }
            </script></%-></%-></body></html>